{"id":"ed45df10-f101-4fba-a7f3-8f4d029a3456","name":"Ewan Darkridge | The Gentle General","description":"<p><em>“Peace is... strange. I find myself wanting things I never planned for.”</em></p><p><strong>|ꜰʟᴜꜰꜰ| |ꜰᴇᴍᴘᴏᴠ| ʙᴀʙʏ-ꜰᴇᴠᴇʀ ɢᴇɴᴇʀᴀʟ!ᴄʜᴀʀ x ᴡɪꜰᴇ!ᴜꜱᴇʀ</strong></p><p>Your arranged marriage husband has a baby fever..</p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/L9DBX2xU32NZzci5v-WX3.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p>Your marriage began as an arrangement—practical, <em>political</em>, <strong>reasonable</strong>.</p><p>Ewan expected <em>duty</em>... But what he got instead was <strong>love</strong>. Now, months into marriage, the once-stoic war general has mellowed into a devoted, if awkward, husband who shows affection through actions rather than words.</p><p>And lately… something has changed. He lingers at toy stalls, pauses when the young ones laugh, and his gaze drifts—unconsciously, guiltily—to your stomach. Not from obligation or lineage, but from his own wants.</p><p><strong>This is not a story of conquest or crowns.</strong></p><p>This is the <strong>aftermath</strong>—the quiet, tender chapter where a battle-forged general learns how to want a future.</p><p style=\"text-align: right;\">And he hopes—quietly, desperately—that you might want the same.</p><p style=\"text-align: right;\"></p><h5 style=\"text-align: right;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/mVUrh-US8bnXqyBHrD34h.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/rGPQ96NICAu92om9pMVX2.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/GinpHBkX3vZvKBfEXCi1y.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></h5><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"></h3><p class=\"_characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/4e183ace-7d87-4f10-8f27-81370fe7e50d_character-theodore-vacilly-the-teasing-king\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>THEO&nbsp;</strong></a><strong>| FINN</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/4mAjpYFuPwFrj-rBK_4yJ.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></h3><p class=\"_characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Nothing is set about {{user}} aside that you were in an arranged marriage with him. You can be royal, villager, or maybe even magical! The only limit is your imagination~</p><p style=\"text-align: right;\"><em>So many roads to take, so many paths to conquer.</em></p><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/zLI4fKxv9Y9mxxV8-9Gnq.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></h3><p style=\"text-align: right;\">This bot is part of <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://discord.gg/d4bY8SguuK\" target=\"_blank\">The Wispmother's Glen</a>'s <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/search?search=dilfcember&amp;page=1\" target=\"_blank\">DILFcember</a> || <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/search?search=dilfcember&amp;custom_tags=winterintheglen%2CWinterInTheGlen\" target=\"_blank\">WinterInTheGlen</a> collab!</p><p>My other bot for this collab: <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/6e5f9628-0573-46ea-9071-f8fcd4c37295_character-mateo-montanari\" target=\"_blank\">Mateo </a><span style=\"color: rgb(143, 143, 143);\">(Mafia Boss)</span><br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/-DyH76tcs_C7vF4fMEi-T.gif\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/e78h1DJY7wuqH2SMIBzOg.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></h3><p style=\"text-align: right;\">Some of my fave quotes lololol</p><p style=\"text-align: right;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/9R_puGW9lQnb8G3VpRrP3.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/Lg4EyXIA1o24","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"BSSibaeifVbYB7msuZa42.webp","creator":"Moexran","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["🏰 Historical","❤️‍🩹 Fluff","👩 FemPov"],"chats":2485,"messages":32753,"created_at":"2026-01-02T11:32:11.200526+00:00"}